- cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms) is relevant as the paper uses mathematical models to analyze network data. 
- cs.CYBER (Cybersecurity and Privacy) is a possibility as the paper studies conflict networks, which may have implications for cybersecurity. 
- cs.GT (Computer Science and Game Theory) is also a possibility as the paper uses game theory concepts to study competition networks.
